as Jefferson High School]]\nImage:Kennedy High School (Los Angeles).jpg|[[John F. Kennedy High School (Los Angeles, California)|John F. Kennedy High School]]\nFile:Robert F Kennedy Community Schools from Wilshire pocket park centered.jpg|[[Robert F. Kennedy Community Schools]]\nImage:Los Angeles HS Night.jpg|[[Los Angeles High School]] \nFile:Reseda High School.JPG|[[Reseda High School]]\nImage:Roybal_Learning_Center.jpg|[[Edward R. Roybal Learning Center]]\nImage:Taft High School Woodland Hills.JPG|[[William Howard Taft High School (Los Angeles, California)|William Howard Taft High School]]\nImage:Van Nuys High School 2008.JPG|[[Van Nuys High School]]\nImage:West Adams Prep HS.jpg|[[West Adams Preparatory High School]]\n</gallery>\n\n===Continuation high schools===\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-break}}\n*[[Jane Addams High School|Addams High School]]\n*[[Angel's Gate High School]]\n*[[Benjamin Franklin High School (Continuation High School)|Benjamin Franklin High School]]\n*[[Avalon High School]]\n*[[Boyle Heights High School]]\n*[[Central High School (Continuation High School)|Central High School]]\n*[[Cheviot Hills High School]]\n*[[Del Rey High School]]\n*[[Douglas High School (Continuation High School)|Douglas High School]]\n*[[East Valley Continuation High School]]\n*[[Eagle Tree Continuation High School]]\n*[[Earhart High School]]\n*[[Einstein High School (Continuation High School)|Einstein High School]]\n*[[Ellington High School (Continuation High School)|Ellington High School]] (Westmont)\n*[[Evergreen High School (Continuation High School)|Evergreen High School]]\n{{col-break}}\n*[[Grey High School (California)|Grey High School]]\n*[[Highland Park High School (Continuation High School)|Highland Park High School]]\n*[[Hope High School (California)|Hope High School]]\n*[[Independence High School (Continuation High School)|Independence High School]]\n*[[John R. Wooden High School]]\n*[[Leonis High School]]\n*[[Lewis High School (Los Angeles)|Lewis High School]]\n*[[London High School (Los Angeles)|London High School]]\n*[[Metropolitan High School]]\n*[[Mission High School (Continuation High School)|Mission High School]]\n*[[Moneta High School]]\n*[[Monterey High School (Continuation High School)|Monterey High School]]\n*[[Mt. Lukens High School]]\n*[[Newmark High School]]\n{{col-break}}\n*[[Odyssey High School]]\n*[[Owensmouth High School]]\n*[[Patton High School]]\n*[[Phoenix High School (Continuation High School)|Phoenix High School]]\n*[[Pueblo de Los Angeles High School]]\n*[[Rodia High School]]\n*[[Rogers High School (Continuation High School)|Rogers High School]]\n*[[San Antonio High School]]\n*[[Stoney Point High School]]\n*[[Thoreau High School]]\n*[[Truth High School]]\n*[[View Park Continuation High School]]\n*[[Walt Whitman High School (Los Angeles)|Walt Whitman High School]]\n*[[Young High School]]\n{{col-end}}<onlyinclude>\n\n====Alternative high schools====\n\n</onlyinclude>\n[[Image:Orthopaedic Hospital MMHS.jpg|thumb|[[Orthopaedic Hospital Medical Magnet High School]]]]\n[[Image:Maywoodacademy.jpg|thumb|[[Maywood Academy High School]]]]\n[[Image:Camino Nuevo Charter MS.jpg|thumb|[[Camino Nuevo Charter Academy]]]]\n<onlyinclude>\n*[[Animo Locke Technology High School]]\n*[[\u00c1nimo South Los Angeles Charter High School|Animo South Los Angeles]] (Westmont)\n*[[Animo Venice Charter High School]]\n*[[Francisco Bravo Medical Magnet High School]]\n*[[California Academy for LS#2|California Academy for LS #2]]\n*[[Camino Nuevo High School]]\n*[[Central City Value]]\n*[[College Ready Academy High School]]\n*[[Crenshaw Arts Technical]]\n*[[Daniel Pearl Magnet High School]]\n*[[De La Hoya Animo High School]]\n*[[Downtown Magnets High School]]\n*[[Discovery Charter Preparatory]]\n*[[East Los Angeles Renaissance Academy]]\n*[[High School for the Visual and Performing Arts]] (formerly known as Central Los Angeles High Area School #9), opened September 2009<ref>http://www.laschools.org/project-status/one-project?project_numb